Module scenebuilder.editors

Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.editors.control

  • Interface Summary
    Interface Description
    EditorItem
    A PropertyEditor based on a list handles a list of EditorItem (for instance StyleEditor handles a list of styles).
    EditorItemDelegate
    Defines the communication interface between an EditorItem and its editor.
